---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="content-shell py-12 md:py-16 space-y-10 max-w-2xl">

    <header class="space-y-4 border-b border-[color:var(--color-border)] pb-8">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Tanmay Satvik</h1>
      <p class="text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
        Penultimate year BBA LL.B (Hons.) student at MAIMS, GGSIPU, New Delhi.
        Graduating 2027.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I am a law student concentrating in corporate law and contract drafting,
        with hands-on experience across arbitration chambers, trademark practice,
        High Court internships, and transactional advisory.
      </p>
      <p>
        <em>Almost a Footnote</em> is where I think in public — close readings of
        legal problems I have worked through, observations from practice, and
        arguments that are still being refined. A CV lists what I have done.
        This is how I think.
      </p>
      <p>
        My primary interests are corporate law, dispute resolution, and
        intellectual property — particularly the intersection of drafting
        precision and strategic legal thinking.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4 border-t border-[color:var(--color-border)] pt-8">
      <p class="eyebrow">Experience</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-ink)] font-medium">Stellar Advisors</span> — Regulatory research, contract drafting, FEMA/cross-border advisory · 2025</li>
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-ink)] font-medium">Company Vakil</span> — Trademark filing, cease & desist, objection replies · 2025</li>
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-ink)] font-medium">Dewan & Dewan Law Chambers</span> — Arbitration research (ICC, SIAC, ISDS) · 2025</li>
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-ink)] font-medium">Jharkhand High Court</span> — Judicial internship under H.M.J Ananda Sen · 2025</li>
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-ink)] font-medium">Office of the Advocate General, Jharkhand</span> — Constitutional and statutory research · 2025</li>
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-ink)] font-medium">Alpha Legal Consultants</span> — Armed Forces Tribunal, service law · 2025</li>
        <li><span class="text-[color:var(--color-ink)] font-medium">Chambers of Chaitanya Singh</span> — Criminal procedure, Delhi HC observation · 2024</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4 border-t border-[color:var(--color-border)] pt-8">
      <p class="eyebrow">Writing</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <li>Terrorism in Financial Crime by Money Laundering</li>
        <li>Law and Biotechnology: Landmark Judgments in India — SYAR India</li>
        <li>ED and BBC: A Chronology of Events — Vidhi Parivartan</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3 border-t border-[color:var(--color-border)] pt-8">
      <p class="eyebrow">Read</p>
      <a href="/blog" class="underline underline-offset-4 text-sm">
        View all writing
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>
</BaseLayout>
